msgstr "ປະສົບການເຮັດວຽກທີ່ຜ່ານມາ"

#. module: hr_recruitment_survey
#: model_terms:survey.survey,description:hr_recruitment_survey.survey_recruitment_form
msgid "Please answer those questions to help recruitment officers to preprocess your application."
msgstr ""
"ກະລຸນາຕອບຄຳຖາມເຫຼົ່ານີ້ ເພື່ອຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ເຈົ້າໜ້າທີ່ສັນຫາບຸກຄະລາກອນ ດຳເນີນການກວດສອບໃບສະໝັກຂອງທ່ານໃນເບື້ອ"
"ງຕົ້ນ."

#. module: hr_recruitment_survey
#: model_terms:survey.question,description:hr_recruitment_survey.survey_recruitment_form_p1
msgid ""
"Please fill information about you: who you are, what are your education, experience, and activities.\n"
"    It will help us managing your application."
msgstr ""
"ກະລຸນາຕື່ມຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບທ່ານ: ທ່ານແມ່ນໃຜ, ການສຶກສາ, ປະສົບການ ແລະ ກິດຈະກຳຂອງທ່ານມີຫຍັງແດ່.\n"
"    ມັນຈະຊ່ວຍໃຫ້ພວກເຮົາຈັດການໃບສະໝັກຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ດີຂຶ້ນ."

#. module: hr_recruitment_survey
#. odoo-python
#: code:addons/hr_recruitment_survey/models/hr_applicant.py:0
#, python-format
